text: Sandra Huggett (born 20 September 1973 in Surrey, England) is an English actress best known for her roles in the Channel 5 soap opera Family Affairs, and ITV's Coronation Street. She grew up in Ross-On-Wye, Herefordshire, but now lives in North London. == Other websites == * Category:1973 births Category:English television actors Category:People from Herefordshire Category:Actors from Surrey Category:Living people
